<subSubSection id="C32E6506091BFFB3FCF8F5F6FBD9FA8B" pageId="5" pageNumber="106" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="8B8B368D091BFFB3FCF8F5F6FCE3FC4B" blockId="5.[811,1456,981,1325]" box="[813,887,981,1007]" pageId="5" pageNumber="106">NOTES</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8B8B368D091BFFB3FCF8F5D7FBD9FA8B" blockId="5.[811,1456,981,1325]" pageId="5" pageNumber="106">
<taxonomicName id="4C344D0E091BFFB3FCF8F5D7FBDBFBA8" box="[813,1103,1012,1038]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Nephrodesmus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="5" pageNumber="106" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="hochreutineri">
<emphasis id="B940EA9F091BFFB3FCF8F5D7FBDBFBA8" box="[813,1103,1012,1038]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="106">Nephrodesmus hochreutineri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
et 
<taxonomicName id="4C344D0E091BFFB3FBB8F5D7FA3BFBA8" box="[1133,1455,1012,1038]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Arthroclianthus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="5" pageNumber="106" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="macrobotryosus">
<emphasis id="B940EA9F091BFFB3FBB8F5D7FA3BFBA8" box="[1133,1455,1012,1038]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="106">Arthroclianthus macrobotryosus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
ont été longtemps confondus en raison d’un doute émis par 
<bibRefCitation id="EFA54B7C091BFFB3FCF9F217FB8EFBE9" author="HOCHREUTINER B. P. G." box="[812,1050,1076,1103]" pageId="5" pageNumber="106" pagination="30 - 46" refId="ref8910" refString="HOCHREUTINER B. P. G. 1909. - Monographia generis Arthroclianthi Baill. Annuaire du Conservatoire et du Jardin botaniques de Geneve 13: 30 - 46. https: // biodiversitylibrary. org / page / 36634375" type="journal article" year="1909">Hochreutiner (1909)</bibRefCitation>
sur l’appartenance des échantillons 
<emphasis id="B940EA9F091BFFB3FCFAF277FC53FBC8" box="[815,967,1108,1134]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="106">Vieillard 2549</emphasis>
(
<typeStatus id="548F882F091BFFB3FC04F277FBA7FBC9" box="[977,1075,1108,1135]" pageId="5" pageNumber="106">holotype</typeStatus>
) et 
<emphasis id="B940EA9F091BFFB3FB83F277FB7AFBC8" box="[1110,1262,1108,1134]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="106">Vieillard 2550</emphasis>
à la même espèce. Cette dernière récolte fut toutefois exclue de 
<taxonomicName id="4C344D0E091BFFB3FAD1F256FA3AFB28" box="[1284,1454,1140,1166]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Nephrodesmus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="5" pageNumber="106" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="hochreutineri">
<emphasis id="B940EA9F091BFFB3FAD1F256FA3AFB28" box="[1284,1454,1140,1166]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="106">N. hochreutineri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
par 
<bibRefCitation id="EFA54B7C091BFFB3FC8DF2B7FB80FB08" author="SCHINDLER A. K." box="[856,1044,1172,1198]" pageId="5" pageNumber="106" pagination="251 - 253" refId="ref9957" refString="SCHINDLER A. K. 1926. - Desmodii generumque affinium species et combinationes novae II. Repertorium Specierum Novarum Regni Vegetabilis 22: 251 - 253. https: // doi. org / 10.1002 / fedr. 19260221306" type="journal article" year="1926">Schindler (1926)</bibRefCitation>
. Deux rameaux distincts sont visibles sur la part 
<emphasis id="B940EA9F091BFFB3FC75F297FBAEFB68" box="[928,1082,1204,1230]" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="106">Vieillard 2549</emphasis>
de l’herbier de NY, correspondant bien à la même espèce. De plus amples explications relatives à cette confusion sont fournies sous le paragraphe 
<taxonomicName id="4C344D0E091BFFB3FAFBF2D0FBD9FA8B" authority="Hochr." authorityName="Hochr." class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Arthroclianthus" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="5" pageNumber="106" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="macrobotryosus">
<emphasis id="B940EA9F091BFFB3FAFBF2D0FC6DFA8B" italics="true" pageId="5" pageNumber="106">Arthroclianthus macrobotryosus</emphasis>
Hochr.
</taxonomicName>
</paragraph>
